# --- generated, not source ---
# Regenerated by memory/ingest.py -- data_ids are tied to whoever's local
# Cognee database ran the ingest, meaningless (and misleading) in a fresh
# clone. Same for graph.html, which is a snapshot of one local graph.
memory/manifest.json
memory/graph.html

